CLOVER TO DO LIST
Last updated 7 Jan 2019

The following list describes known updates and issue resolutions that will be included in the future.

1. Addition of environmental assessment module
  - Allows the user to assess the greenhouse gas emissions of systems that have been simulated and optimised
  - Associated edits to Optimisation.py to integrate
2. Addition of power analysis module
  - Allows the user to analyse peak power demand, in addition to energy demand
  - Associated edits to various files
3. Bug fixes
  - Compatibility assurance with Windows
